column1: That mysterious person should be somewhere around this area
according to the Momosame sisters.
Would you happen to be looking for me,
wind-manipulating miko?
So you finally show yourself,
the mastermind of this incident!
What do you mean, mastermind?
Isn't that pushing it a bit?
Aren’t you the one who helped the Momosame sisters and amplified this incident?
Well, I only wanted to do some sightseeing in Gensokyo.
On my way, I also helped two troubled people of my own volition.
Did I do something wrong?
Stop making excuses!
You are an outsider that can freely cross Gensokyo's Border.
If I keep leaving you unattended, there is no doubt that you'll be planning something serious!
Before that happens, I’ll make sure to exterminate you!
Exterminate me?
Are you worried those things from the Outside World could destroy Gensokyo's peace?
It seems that you know nothing about the Outside World.
I'm quite familiar with the Outside World.
What?
That's because I’m a human that came from the outside world too.
Interesting…
I wonder what kind of danmaku a human from the outside world would use?
I would really like to know.
Then a danmaku duel it is!
So, a shrine maiden who manipulates wind?
What a coincidence!
Well then, I will only use a quarter of my strength,
and let you experience the true power of a storm!
